<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Slide</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background-image: url('https://previews.123rf.com/images/romastudio/romastudio1607/romastudio160700145/60755685-healthy-berries-background-old-paper-with-fresh-strawberry-and-mint-leaf-on-wooden-table-copy-space.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .slide-container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px 0px #888888;
            max-width: 1800px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            background-color: #044b19;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #0b491e;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #0b491e;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .centered-links {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .bubble-link {
            background-color: #87e2a2;
            color: rgb(17, 17, 17);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 5px 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .bmi-container {
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .bmi-container h2 {
            background-color:  rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            color: rgb(36, 35, 35);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .bmi-container form {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px 0px #888888;
        }

        .slideshow-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 400px auto;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: -170px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .mySlides {
            display: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .slide-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

    </style>
    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="slide-container">
        <h1>FitBit</h1>
        <div class="centered-links">
            <a href="http://localhost:3500/about" class="bubble-link">Rólunk</a>
            <a href="http://localhost:3500/register" class="bubble-link">Regisztráció</a>
            <a href="http://localhost:3500/login" class="bubble-link">Bejelentkezés</a>
        </div>
        <p>Az egészség a legfontosabb dolog az életben. Vigyázz magadra, és kövesd ezeket az egészségügyi tippeket:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Rendszeresen mozogj.</li>
            <li>Egyél egészségesen és kiegyensúlyozottan.</li>
            <li>Aludj legalább 7-8 órát minden éjszaka.</li>
            <li>Kerüld a stresszt és relaxálj rendszeresen.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="slideshow-container">
        <div class="mySlides">
            <img class="slide-img" src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.3v0zA_ULGfj5LHLGzXfwdQHaE8?pid=ImgDet&rs=1&adlt=strict" alt="Slide 1">
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides">
            <img class="slide-img" src="https://domina.parameter.sk/sites/default/files/photos/taplalekpiramis.jpg" alt="Slide 2">
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides">
            <img class="slide-img" src="https://asset.kompas.com/crops/To8LLlJU-TQuUC90KEimWl4I2zc=/20x0:992x648/490x326/data/photo/2018/01/14/2342554562.jpg" alt="Slide 3">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bmi-container">
        <h2>BMI Kalkulátor</h2>
        <form>
            <label for="weight">Testsúly (kg):</label>
            <input type="number" id="weight" placeholder="Adja meg a testsúlyát" required>

            <label for="height">Magasság (cm):</label>
            <input type="number" id="height" placeholder="Adja meg a magasságát" required>

            <button type="button" onclick="calculateBMI()">Számol</button>

            <p>Önnek a BMI-je: <span id="bmi-result"></span></p>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script>
        let slideIndex = 0;
        showSlides();

        function showSlides() {
            const slides = document.getElementsByClassName("mySlides");
            for (let i = 0; i < slides.length; i++) {
                slides[i].style.display = "none";
            }
            slideIndex++;
            if (slideIndex > slides.length) { slideIndex = 1 }
            slides[slideIndex - 1].style.display = "block";
            setTimeout(showSlides, 2000);
        }

        function calculateBMI() {
            const weight = parseFloat(document.getElementById("weight").value);
            const height = parseFloat(document.getElementById("height").value) / 100;
            const bmi = weight / (height * height);
            document.getElementById("bmi-result").textContent = bmi.toFixed(2);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
